      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This Z32 Nissan 300ZX Twin Turbo is a prime example of 90s engineering, featuring the formidable VG30DETT engine with its dual-overhead-cam, twin-turbocharged configuration. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated viscous limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle benefits from a functional Super HICAS four-wheel steering system and updated vacuum lines to maintain intake charge integrity and peak boost response. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and a cooling system overhaul. The suspension utilizes multi-link geometry with upgraded bushings, providing a firm, communicative chassis that excels in high-speed cornering. This is a driver-focused machine that balances raw forced-induction performance with sophisticated Japanese grand-touring dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
